<view class="page">
  <view class="status-bar" style="height: {{statusBarHeight}}px"></view>
  <view class="nav">
    <view class="back-btn" bindtap="onBackTap">◀</view>
    <text class="title">注册新商家</text>
  </view>
  <view class="content">
    <view class="field">
      <text class="label">店铺名称</text>
      <input class="input" placeholder="请输入店铺名称" bindinput="onNameInput" />
    </view>
    <view class="field">
      <text class="label">管理员邀请码</text>
      <input class="input" placeholder="请输入邀请码" bindinput="onCodeInput" />
    </view>
    <view class="field">
      <text class="label">登录账号</text>
      <input class="input" type="text" placeholder="请输入登录账号（用于密码登录）" bindinput="onAccountInput" />
    </view>
    <view class="field">
      <text class="label">登录密码</text>
      <input class="input" type="password" placeholder="请输入登录密码（至少6位）" bindinput="onPasswordInput" />
    </view>
    <view class="field">
      <text class="label">确认密码</text>
      <input class="input" type="password" placeholder="请再次输入登录密码" bindinput="onConfirmPasswordInput" />
    </view>
    <view class="tip">
      <view class="tip-item">• 商家注册：填写店铺名称、邀请码、登录账号和密码</view>
      <view class="tip-item">• 管理端登录：仅填写登录账号和密码（店铺和邀请码留空）</view>
      <view class="tip-item">• 设置账号密码后可在不同设备使用账号密码登录</view>
    </view>
    <view class="btn primary" bindtap="onSubmit">提交</view>
  </view>
</view>


